 Ice Spice 因涉嫌侵犯版权被起诉https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-sued-for-alleged-copyright-infringement-3572842?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ice-spice-sued-for-alleged-copyright-infringementTom Skinner Thu, 18 Jan 2024 10:17:24 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3572842 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ice Spice 现场表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位说唱歌手被指控抄袭她 2023 年单曲《In Ha Mood》的部分歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-sued-for-alleged-copyright-infringement-3572842">Ice Spice 因涉嫌侵犯版权而被起诉的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ice Spice 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/IceSpice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a>因涉嫌侵犯其 2023 年单曲“In Ha Mood”的版权而被起诉。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/ice-spice-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-in-ha-mood-1234948699/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》报道</em></a>，两名音乐家已对纽约说唱歌手（真名 Isis Naija Gaston）提起诉讼，声称这首歌侵犯了他们的歌曲《In That Mood》的版权。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/ice-spice-like-project-interview-new-music-spongebob-radar-3385136">Ice Spice：认识互联网上最热门的新说唱歌手</a></strong></li></ul><p>后者由布鲁克林说唱歌手/词曲作者杜瓦尔“D.Chamberz”张伯伦和布朗克斯音响工程师/制作人肯利“Kass The Producer”Carmenate 发行。</p><p>在纽约东区提交的诉状中，两人指控 Gaston Riot 在未经许可或适当的信用的情况下“复制”了《In That Mood》的名字、副歌、副歌、措辞和节奏。</p><p>诉讼称这两首歌“极其相似，不可能纯粹是巧合”。</p><p>它指出：“《In Ha Mood》和《In That Mood》之间的相似之处——包括副歌中使用的关键短语以及在两首歌中以基本相似的方式重复了很多次——以至于根本不合理地相信如果没有先听过《In That Mood》，《In Ha Mood》也可能被创作出来。”</p><p> 《In That Mood》于 2022 年初作为单曲发行。张伯伦于去年 8 月在 Instagram 帖子中首次使用了这首歌曲。这首歌后来出现在 D.Chamberz 的专辑《Boom Bap 2 Drill Rap》中。 </p><p><iframe title="冰香料 - 心情愉快（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RIJbCb1KrOk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="那样的心情" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gluHUnUJrYY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，张伯伦声称他在纽约以及宾夕法尼亚州、西弗吉尼亚州和佛罗里达州等其他州公开表演了至少三打《In That Mood》。</p><p>诉讼称：“据了解并确信，Ice Spice、Riot 和/或其创意团队成员在相关时间段内参加了 In That Mood 的某些公开表演。</p><p> “此外，原告在说唱和嘻哈界很有名，并且与被告有着大量不可否认的联系。”</p><p>张伯伦和卡门纳特正在通过诉讼寻求损害赔偿。</p><p>据报道，Ice Spice 的代表未能立即发表评论。</p><p>去年9月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-2023-mtv-vmas-3496804">Ice Spice在2023年MTV VMA颁奖典礼上获得了最佳新人奖</a>。她还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a>等人一起四次进入公告牌排行榜前十名。</p><p>这位说唱歌手与后者合作制作了现已获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>提名的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-and-ice-spice-share-version-of-barbie-world-from-barbie-soundtrack-3460010">“芭比世界”</a> ，该单曲收录在广受好评的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比</em></a>原声带<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/barbie-soundtrack-review-film-3471113">“芭比：专辑”</a>中。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-has-been-spotted-shooting-a-new-video-in-miami-song-3571754">Ice Spice 最近在佛罗里达州迈阿密拍摄了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-teases-comical-new-song-produced-by-riotusa-latto-3567092">她本月早些时候预演的一首歌曲</a>的新音乐视频。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-sued-for-alleged-copyright-infringement-3572842">Ice Spice 因涉嫌侵犯版权而被起诉的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
